name: Teleportato
description:
My first ever game! This was made over 9 days for the captain disillusion discord's first ever Game Jam.  You play as a potato dropped into a cardboard box.

Low poly potato model from SketchFab - https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/lowpoly-potato-free-f7458371e1fb418487806926d845a7dd

photo of cardboard box in thumbnail created by kstudio - www.freepik.com
